.admin
  .clearfix
    %h3.pull-left Users
    .pull-right.header-button
      = link_to 'Add User', new_admin_user_path, class: 'btn btn-school'
  %p.description
    This section is where the administrator can add/edit other admin users within StudyFinder.  To add a new user click the "Add User" button above.  You will need their unique email and internet_id.  Once a user has been added, they will be able to access the entire admininstration area, so only grant these priveledges to administrative staff.

  %table.table.table-bordered.table-trials
    %thead
      %tr
        %th Name
        %th Email
        %th 
    %tbody
      - if @users.empty?
        %tr
          %td{ colspan: 3 } There are no users loaded. Add users manually using the add button above.
      - @users.each do |u|
        %tr
          %td= u.full_name
          %td= mail_to u.email
          %td{ width: 150 }
            = link_to 'Edit', edit_admin_user_path(u.id), class: 'btn btn-primary'
            = link_to 'Delete', admin_user_path(u.id), method: 'delete', class: 'btn btn-danger', data: { confirm:"Are you sure you want to delete this user?" }